metadata.name: Eternity Imagination Seed
metadata.description:
In the center of an endless space filled with emptiness, There was a "SEED" of imagination floating aimlessly.

The light from the mysterious prism shine brightly and allowed the seed to bloom rapidly infinite.

Anything and everything are starting to create and generate continuously and endlessly.

One young girl combines "IMAGINATION" with reality to tell a story with the tip of her pen.

What exactly is her purpose? No one knew.

Now the story has begun. From zero to "ETERNITY".

"Eternity Imagination Seed"
Series-0 Zone-0 Section-1 #BLUZON909 
Original Artwork by ZakDreaWM

1/1 | 2000 x 3000 pixels | 300 DPI
